overview: The user intends to implement a scroll-to-top button feature on a
  webpage. The button needs to be positioned at the bottom-right, become visible
  only after the user scrolls down the page, and navigate the user back to the
  top of the page upon being clicked. This is an initial request for a new UI
  element with specific behavioral requirements.
